      public <B extends Block> DeferredBlockBuilder<B> register(String name, Supplier<? extends B> sup)
      从类复制的说明: DeferredRegister.Blocks
      Adds a new block to the list of entries to be registered and returns a DeferredHolder that will be populated with the created block automatically.
      覆盖:
      register 在类中 DeferredRegister.Blocks
      参数:
      name - The new block's name. It will automatically have the namespace prefixed.

      返回:
